<plot>"LE CHASE" (19 min. B&amp;W. In poorly spoken French with mangled-English subtitles) Shot in the cinematic style of French New Wave Film, "Le Chase" takes a comic look at the unlikely romance between Hero, an ordinary man trying to bring beauty to the world, and Francie, a street tough trapped in a life of vandalism and petty punkery. With the help of a kindly French Whore and an extreme make over, Hero is able to face his fears and convince Francie's band of hoods, appropriately called "Les Punks," to give up their hooliganism - allowing Francie to unlock the heart that beats beneath her punkish shell.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?321977</url></doc>
